sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { AboContainer, Abowrapper, AboRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, Heading, Subtitle, TopLine, BtnWrap, ImgWrap, Img, } from "./AboutElements"; import { Button } from "react-scroll"; export const AboutSection = ({ lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, description, img, alt, }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {heading} {description} ); };
